18 (9) A beverage or other product, other than a soft drink or
19 energy drink, that contains plant protein sources.
20 (10) A product, other than a soft drink or energy drink, that:
21 (A) is fortified with a vitamin or mineral; and
22 (B) contains a source of protein.
23 (g) If the office of the secretary determines that a waiver or
24 authorization by a federal agency is needed to implement this
25 section, the office:
26 (1) shall, not later than July 1, 2027, request the necessary
27 waiver or authorization; and
28 (2) may delay implementation of this section until the waiver
29 or authorization is granted.
